    "navbar": "LOG INSIGN UP",
    "text": "LOG INSIGN UP\nSCORES\nSCHEDULES\nGET SCHEDULES\nZJK\nCounty\nSports Zone\nCounty Sports Zone is the online home for your high school sports community. County Sports Zone is the best way to stay informed about what’s going on in high school sports – whether it’s last minute scheduling changes, finding a local trainer, or sharing highlights from last night’s game. There are so many ways our high school sports community can update us, we just need a better way to connect.\nGet in THE ZONE\nShare highlights, scores, reports, and much more of all high school sports.\nENTER THE ZONE\nEffective\nThe easiest way to find much-needed high school sports updates.\nLocal\nInformation that is meaningful to you provided by your community.\nRewarding\nA community celebrating the passion of high school sports.\nDon't miss out on all the action in your community\nJOIN NOW\nScores\nSchedules\nThe Zone\nPlayoffs\nContact Us\nLog In\nAbout CSZ\nAdvertise\nAdmin Login\nPrivacy Policy",
